  "faqFeaturesGuide": "What can ClashKing app do?",
  "faqFeaturesGuideDescription": "Take your Clash of Clans experience to the next level! ClashKing app delivers beautiful, fast access to all your stats and clan data - perfect for players who do not have Discordand those who prefer a sleek mobile experience:",
  "faqAppDevelopmentNotice": "We're actively developing new features to make the app even better. Your feedback helps us improve!",
  "faqFeaturesPlayerTitle": "Player Statistics",
  "faqFeaturesPlayerDescription": "Track your progress, achievements, and legend league performance",
